java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<CoverElement>, java.util.Collection<CoverElement>, java.util.Set<CoverElement>
public class Cover
extends HashSet<CoverElement>

A Cover is a set of CoverElement, which means one of the element should be satisfied. If an inconsistent element is being inserted to this cover, it will be discarded automatically.
